The paper focuses on a method for identifying original versions of cloned components in software development, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also employs techniques such as file similarity computation and code search, which are relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper addresses security vulnerabilities, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR), and uses a large collection of software packages, which relates to databases (cs.DB).
